{"type": "article", "id": 15721, "title": "卡通门贴", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-08T07:24:24Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 88, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021355499eTm7f1ARIOPrVBp.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t芬兰设计品牌 Made of Sundays 推出了一系列卡通动物图案的房门贴纸，用简洁的线条使单调而常规的门变得丰富有趣。采用可生物分解的聚酯纤维织物贴纸，安全环保，使低龄儿童也能使用。而这组贴纸的亮点还是在小动物呆萌的表情，让人跟着一起放空发呆。而寥寥可数是线条不仅契合了不同动物的特点，同时保持了门窗和玻璃通透的原貌。<a href=\"http://www.etsy.com/shop/MadeofSundays?zanpid=2086397019022648320&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_source=zanox&amp;utm_campaign=eu_buyer&amp;utm_content=2147023\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143122KQv8StRyz0u3kZHb.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"550\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143124bBVMX6fUul2sFY8k.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"550\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143125HBwkiz7qPIuEDras.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"550\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143125krGPEhXMutdlHsfe.jpg\" width=\"870\" height=\"558\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.64137931\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}